summary: So,more dream creature!Altought this one really scared me,but maybe it was more because of the ominous/familiar settings of the...
body:
So,more dream creature!Altought this one really scared me,but maybe it was more because of the ominous/familiar settings of the dream I had.
I took some liberties to add elements to it,like the tentacles sprouting from it’s mouth,and the yellow eyes inside it.

Basically,I dreamed I was right outside the door of my house,just,standing there,next to a bench that’s always there,and it was night time.since the door was closed I took several steps and advanced,then I noticed in the corner of the garden,the place were usually there are two vases and irl,there is always firebugs (the red and black insects) always chilling in this corner.Ihis time,I saw a thick looking web over the hole on one of the vase,and there was two tiny spiders with a huge abdomen,trapping them and moving very quickly on their web,and there was a group of egg in the middle of said web.I heard loud shrieks from there,so I just looked away and kept on walking.Then I neared toward the gate in front of my house,and I saw a cat accompanied with this weird creature ,seeming to try to pull something from the other’s mouth.A mouse,maybe.Kinda like rope tugging wayThe weird creature had roughly the size of a cat,and had no eyes,ofc.Yet it saw me,and jumped from the top of the gate and immediately neared toward me. For some reason,I started to feel really scared,seeing the way it’s weird shaped tail was wriggling.I stepped backward,then,a faceless,grey figure appeared next to me,with only a mouth then spoke “You can ask anything you want from it.” I looked at them,then back at the creature standing right in front of me.I replied “anything?” and they answered “yes”. I remained silent and was about to speak up,but the grey figure interrupted me “But be careful,as soon as your wish is granted,it will take your life.” There was a moment of heavy silence,staring at the still creature. “what will you do?"then it went downhill and off topic when i suddenly dreamed of miles tails,a character from sega trying to put colorful sculptures upside down to keep the earth from exploding or something,and the creature was there,then someone started screaming,and another person said that anyone who scream near the creature is gonna die,killed by the creature or something.
(wooo description copy-past)
